*** OperServ Operator Help - Command: GLOBAL ***
Allows IRCops to send messages to all users on the network.
The message will be sent from the nick Azzurra.
 
Syntax: GLOBAL target message
 
target can be a host, a language (IT, US, ES, FR), or a server.
Use ALL as target to send the message to all users.
 
Examples:
/os GLOBAL *.home.com Please don't dump me after I like you!
/os GLOBAL fastweb.azzurra.chat This server is rebooting in 5 minutes.
/os GLOBAL IT Messaggio riservato agli italiani
 
This command is limited to Services Administrators.
*** End of OHelp ***